  "prompt": "What are the best web design firms in New York?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, several web design firms in New York are highly regarded for their creativity, expertise, and client satisfaction. Here\u2019s a list of some of the top firms:\n\n1. **Huge** - Known for its innovative design and technology solutions, Huge works with a variety of clients, including major brands.\n\n2. **Frog Design** - An influential design firm that focuses on experience design and branding, Frog has a strong portfolio and global presence.\n\n3. **R/GA** - This agency is well-known for blending technology, design, and marketing, providing comprehensive digital solutions.\n\n4. **Blue Fountain Media** - Specializing in web design and digital marketing, Blue Fountain Media has a strong reputation for delivering effective online solutions.\n\n5. **Toptal** - While not a traditional agency, Toptal connects clients with top freelance web designers and developers, enabling personalized and flexible design services.\n\n6. **Spur** - Known for their focus on branding and design, Spur provides tailored solutions that resonate with their client\u2019s audience.\n\n7. **ThoughtBot** - Specializing in product design and development, ThoughtBot has a reputation for creating user-friendly and effective digital experiences.\n\n8. **Hatch** - This firm focuses on modern design and user experience, crafting visually appealing and functional websites.\n\n9. **Mediacurrent** - Known for their Drupal expertise, Mediacurrent provides web design and development solutions alongside digital strategy.\n\n10. **Clever Creative** - A full-service agency, Clever Creative offers a blend of branding, design, and marketing services with a focus on user experience.\n\nWhen selecting a web design firm, it\u2019s important to consider your specific needs, budget, and the firm\u2019s expertise in your industry. It may also be beneficial to look at their portfolios and client testimonials to find a firm that aligns well with your vision.",
